These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different games are played: poker, bridge, snooker, scrabble
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, quad-bike, tram, airplane
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, mexican, pakistani, russian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, horse, rat
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 2. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
 3. the brazilian is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 7. the mexican is the person playing snooker##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the person driving the airplane##2
10. the person playing poker is the owner of the rat##1
11. the person driving the tram is the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | snooker  | poker    | scrabble    | bridge   |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | snowmobile   | tram       | airplane    |
| Nationality   | mexican | brazilian | russian    | pakistani |
| Pet           | hamster | rat       | chinchilla | horse     |

