.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, fantasy, crime, western
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, may, january, december
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, cycling, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 7. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | scientific  | fantasy    | crime     | western       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | baking   | collecting |
| Birthday   | january | september   | may   | december    |
| Sport         | cycling | volleyball  | biathlon | climbing   |

