.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, paramedic, social-worker, writer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, alhambra, vegafina, old-henry
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, brown, coral, apricot
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 2. the alhambra-smoker is the social-worker##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 4. the librarian is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 5. the person drinking juice is the writer##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
 7. the person who likes purple is the old-henry-smoker##1
 8. the writer is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
10. the person who likes purple is the person drinking mirinda##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | sprite    | juice      |
| Job           | social-worker | librarian | paramedic | writer     |
| Cigar   | alhambra      | old-henry   | chaman   | vegafina |
| Color           | apricot         | purple       | coral  | brown       |

