.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, orange, pineapple, spinach
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris, balloon-flower, aconite
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person eating spinach##2
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating kiwi##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 6. the person who growszinnia is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating orange is the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
12. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | pineapple    | spinach      | kiwi          | orange    |
| Flower   | iris | aconite       | balloon-flower | zinnia |
| Beverage     | sprite     | hot-chocolate      | soy-milk     | lemonade |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | snowboarding | skiing        | cricket   |

