 2. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
 3. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
 5. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
 6. the person traveling to new-york is between the german and the person traveling to berlin##2
 7. the person traveling to boston is the person eating cauliflower##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the colombian is on the far right##1
10. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Flower      | daffodil  | aconite    | lily       | tulip       |
| Food          | orange    | cauliflower | artichoke | apple     |
