The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, skydiving, writing
 1. the person eating mango is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of folk is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who's hobby is chess##2
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
 5. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 7. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who growsbellflower##1
 9. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
11. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of house is on the left of the person eating potato##1
13. the fan of indie is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
