.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, video-games
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, blend, montecristo, siglo
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, turquise, chestnut, azure
 1. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 2. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 3. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the blend-smoker is in an even position##4
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
 8. the montecristo-smoker is on the far right##1
 9. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
10. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
11. the siglo-smoker is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice       | hot-chocolate | 7up        | milk        |
| Hobby         | video-games | singing       | card-games | photography |
| Cigar   | siglo     | blend        | oliveros    | montecristo      |
| Color         | turquise     | chestnut    | azure | aquamarine   |

