.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, designer, lawyer, architect
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, french, indonesian, polish
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, wooden, tower
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the architect is the wooden house##1
 2. the wooden house is between the australian and the polish##2
 3. the wooden house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the french##1
 5. the art-deco house is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the designer is the gothic-revival house##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 8. the polish is in an even position##4
 9. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
10. the australian is in an even position##4
11. the australian is on the far right##1
12. the mechanic is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Job   | designer      | mechanic | architect     | lawyer        |
| Nationality   | indonesian | polish  | french     | australian |
| House         | gothic-revival    | art-deco | wooden      | tower |
| Transport     | skateboard | car     | helicopter | bike       |

 